                  <p><notvariant>Sch</notvariant>. That we <normalised orig="geue" auto="true">give</normalised> <normalised orig="vnto" auto="true">unto</normalised> his <normalised orig="Maiestie" auto="true">Majesty</normalised> the <normalised orig="soueraigne" auto="true">sovereign</normalised><lb/>
<normalised orig="honor" auto="true">honour</normalised>, and to his <normalised orig="goodnesse" auto="true">goodness</normalised> the greatest<lb/>
